  <summary date="2018-04-06T19:02:01Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Arbitration Fairness Act of 2018

This bill prohibits a predispute arbitration agreement from being valid or enforceable if it requires arbitration of an employment dispute, consumer dispute, antitrust dispute, or civil rights dispute.</summary>
